                        <interp inst="t18380917-name-282" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE AVIS</persName>
                  </hi>. I went to Mr. Hughes, a stationer, at No. 42, Gilbert. street—the prisoner lodges there, on the first floor—he took me to it him<lb></lb>self—I waited till his wife got up—I went in and found the property—I</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183809170034"></xptr>
               <p>brought away what Mr. Hughes claimed—the prisoner said nothing—he did not deny it.</p>
